            Ameris Bancorp owns and operates the Ameris banking chain. As a bank, Ameris provides banking services to individuals and businesses in Georgia, Florida and Alabama. With more than 40 locations and approximately $1.5 billion in assets, the bank provides a range of retail and commercial banking services. Its personal banking products include certificates of deposit, money market accounts, consumer Internet banking and bill pay, checking and savings accounts and a variety of loans. The bank also offers a variety of business products, such as merchant card services, money market accounts, business Internet banking, checking and savings accounts and loans. Ameris Bancorp has a location in Moultrie, Ga.
          






















