Key people

·Edwin Hortman, Jr., Ameris Bank Chief Executive Officer, Ameris Bancorp President & Chief Executive Officer
·Dennis J. Zember Jr., Ameris Bank Executive Vice President and Chief Operating Officer, Ameris Bancorp Executive Vice President, Chief Operating Officer & Chief Financial Officer
·Andrew B. Cheney, Executive Vice President and Chief Banking Executive for Ameris Bank and Ameris Bancorp
·Lawton E. Bassett, III, Ameris Bank President & Ameris Bancorp Banking Group President
